      "webPublicationDate":"2013-10-16T14:57:02Z",
      "webTitle":"Royal Mail workers vote in favour of strike following privatisation",
      "webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2013/oct/16/royal-mail-workers-vote-favour-strike-privatisation",
